14 SUMMARY
1155 This bill amends the definition of "nuisance dog" to include a dog or wolf hybrid that
1166 disturbs the peace of an individual by excessive barking, howling or yelping, and the
1177 individual is not trespassing on the dog or wolf hybrid owner's or keeper's premises at the
1188 time of the excessive barking, howling or yelping. The bill also explicitly authorizes a
